  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until browned, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the tamarind paste, dry sherry, and coconut milk, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the chicken is cooked through, about 15-20 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles."
